Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.49,0:00:04.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs28\fad(350,0)}7/15 13:55 [櫻見市 櫻見市政廳]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.18,0:00:13.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,市長 本周內解散育幼中心這個決定
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.92,0:00:16.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認為不論怎麼說都太操之過急了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.16,0:00:19.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,市長 請回應
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.64,0:00:24.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的想法也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.75,0:00:28.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一想到被迫離開那裡的孩子們我就深感心痛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.95,0:00:31.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是正如各位所知
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.02,0:00:37.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個養護中心涉嫌藏匿毀壞櫻見塔的主犯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.74,0:00:38.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.84,0:00:43.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我無法相信這樣的養護中心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.68,0:00:45.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嫌疑不過只是嫌疑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.38,0:00:49.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等到問題發生就為時已晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.58,0:00:54.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽著 我真心將這個城市的孩子們當成自己的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.07,0:00:58.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然 這也包括育幼中心裡的孩子們
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.68,0:01:04.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們難道想把孩子們捲進政治鬥爭嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.19,0:01:11.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且孩子們不過是暫時轉移至其他中心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.06,0:01:15.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也會將對孩子們的影響降至最低
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.73,0:01:20.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我反倒不明白反對這項提議的人是居心何在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.73,0:01:27.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望反對的人也能闡述一番
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.50,0:01:34.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼進入裁決階段
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.55,0:01:39.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起立贊成者多數
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.20,0:01:44.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決定廢除母親之家育幼中心

Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.07,0:02:03.63,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}The girl with the sharp thorn in her flesh
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.63,0:02:06.25,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}I meet you at your story
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.26,0:02:11.34,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Behind the hatred there lies a murderous love
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.45,0:02:14.02,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Do you kill your friends
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.02,0:02:16.63,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}If you can fulfill your wish?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.63,0:02:19.25,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Can you die for someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.25,0:02:22.35,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}They are synonymous words
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.35,0:02:24.92,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Life is a game  It's a survival  That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.92,0:02:27.51,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}How do you start?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.51,0:02:30.24,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Time and Space  It's a crossroad  through a gate!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.24,0:02:33.14,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Where do you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.14,0:02:35.62,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}You seek eternal breath
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.69,0:02:37.54,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Why do you need to live?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.54,0:02:42.91,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}We don't know when this world came into being
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.91,0:02:44.78,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}We are the timeleaper
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.78,0:02:47.79,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Nothing's gonna change with you in the world
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.79,0:02:50.82,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Everything will be decided by the rules
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.82,0:02:55.63,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Oh,We are traveling the past and the future through love
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.63,0:02:56.29,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Break out!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.29,0:03:01.34,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Let's dial back all the pains and we will be born again
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.34,0:03:03.96,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}I wanna see the stars with you
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.96,0:03:07.02,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Over the miracle
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.02,0:03:13.83,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}It's not a Dead END


